com.ociweb.xml

Interface StartTagWAX

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommonWAX, ElementWAX
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WAX

    public interface StartTagWAX
extends ElementWAX
    This interface defines the methods that can be called after the beginning of a start tag has been output, but it (the start tag itself, not a terminating end tag) has been closed.
